78701 claims a lien, in accordance to Chapter 55 of the Texas Property Code, for the treatment, care and maintenance of the following
injured individual:1
MICKEY BUSTOS (3114485640)
6201 WIDELEAF DR AUSTIN, TX 7872
On or about 11/13/2021, the individual allegedly sustained personal injuries and sought treatment for said injuries within seventy-
two (72) hours as a result of the accident, Treatment, care and maintenance was provided by DELL SETON MEDICAL CENTER for a
period of no longer than one hundred days, and the amount due is based upon charges that are reasonable and at a regular rate for
such services. The name(s) of the person(s), jf-known, alleged to be liable for the damages arising from said injury are:
This lien will attach to any cause of action or clain the injured individual may have against another person for the individual's injuries;
